pages.Contact.about_page.about_section.c: FitWorking is a web platform that connects people with modern and accessible fitness centers. Our goal is to make quality facilities, qualified trainers, and personalized experiences accessible, regardless of location. FitWorking is not just a website, it's a meeting point for those seeking an active and healthy lifestyle, promoting a community united by well-being.
pages.Contact.about_page.contact_section: If you have questions, suggestions, or need assistance, don't hesitate to write to us. We’ll get back to you as soon as possible!
pages.Faq1.why_fitworking.articles.0.tit: Do I need to be in shape before joining FitWorking?
pages.Faq1.why_fitworking.articles.0.con: You don’t need to prepare before starting; functional training is designed to help you progress from wherever you are, with the support of a community that encourages you every step of the way. The best time to start is now!
pages.Faq1.why_fitworking.articles.1.tit: How will my body change after joining FitWorking?
pages.Faq1.why_fitworking.articles.1.con: Your goals and effort will determine your results. At FitWorking, our users often feel stronger and significantly improve their endurance. Combined with our nutrition and wellness recommendations, you’ll also notice improvements in your overall health and productivity.
pages.Faq1.why_fitworking.articles.2.tit: What should I expect in my first FitWorking class?
pages.Faq1.why_fitworking.articles.2.con: It’s normal to feel nervous – and that’s okay! From knowing what to bring to meeting your coach and learning the exercises, we’ll guide you through the entire process.

pages.Index.banner.description: We combine functional training, sports events, and an active lifestyle in a space designed to inspire you. Join our community and become the best version of yourself.
pages.Index.for_you_section.title: FitWorking is for you
pages.Index.for_you_section.articles.0.t: A father's promise: lose 38 kilos to run with his kids
pages.Index.for_you_section.articles.0.d: Now it's much easier to walk, climb stairs, and chase after the kids.
pages.Index.for_you_section.articles.1.t: Go beyond the physical by building mental strength and resilience
pages.Index.for_you_section.articles.1.d: Engaging in physically challenging exercise helps build mental toughness when life gets tough.
pages.Index.for_you_section.articles.2.t: Sense of belonging: A community walking with you towards change
pages.Index.for_you_section.articles.2.d: When we share the effort, the journey becomes easier. Here, every achievement is celebrated and every stumble is supported. You're not alone: we’re a community moving forward together.
pages.Index.how_it_works.title: How does it work?
pages.Index.how_it_works.subtitle: If you're wondering how we work and what our service includes, let me explain briefly below.
pages.Index.how_it_works.benefits.0.desc: We'll listen to you and adapt this healthy lifestyle to your current situation to ensure success.
pages.Index.how_it_works.benefits.1.desc: We'll give you easy, healthy eating guidelines. No more unsustainable, boring diets.
pages.Index.how_it_works.benefits.2.desc: You’ll improve in the most efficient way possible—without risking your health, time, or money.
pages.Index.how_it_works.benefits.3.desc: Here, you'll not only improve your body and health, but also get to know yourself better and grow mentally.
pages.Index.how_it_works.benefits.4.desc: You might start here to reach your goals, but you’ll stay because of the great vibe in our classes.
pages.Index.how_it_works.benefits.5.desc: Let’s be honest, it’s hard to do it on your own. We’ll be the push you need to get started!
pages.Index.how_it_works.benefits.6.desc: We’ll find the best time for you, so coming to train won’t feel like a puzzle.
pages.Index.how_it_works.benefits.7.desc: On weekends, we organize outdoor activities and gatherings to enjoy being active and sharing experiences.
